  "detailed_description": "<h1>Join our discord</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>∷ Indulge in fast-paced battles for an exhilarating combat experience.<br>∷ Choose from four unique characters to transform your gameplay experience.<br>∷ Craft varying battle experiences with 9 unique weapons tailored to each character.<br>∷ Forge a distinctive build through a rich mix of character talents, abilities, and artifacts.<br>∷ Enjoy the thrill of random weaon bonues and relentless reforging.<br>∷ Use your custom builds to climb the difficulty levels and confront a variety of mysterious monsters and Bosses.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2439710/extras/e8efe0862c8cae6003b7cd26bd59a445.poster.avif?t=1727170517\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2439710/extras/e8efe0862c8cae6003b7cd26bd59a445.webm?t=1727170517\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2439710/extras/e8efe0862c8cae6003b7cd26bd59a445.mp4?t=1727170517\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Strategize with Weapons, Customize Your Combat Style</h2></strong><br>The game features four distinct characters, each with 9 different weapons that can alter their moves. With 3 advanced effects for each type of attack - Basic Attack, Dash, and Ultimate - you can unleash multiple levels of damage, teleportation, disruption, buffs, and more. Engage in proactive combat and enjoy exhilarating, fast-paced battles.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2439710/extras/eece372556cb7d62382eaab372d096f5.poster.avif?t=1727170517\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2439710/extras/eece372556cb7d62382eaab372d096f5.webm?t=1727170517\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2439710/extras/eece372556cb7d62382eaab372d096f5.mp4?t=1727170517\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Forge Exclusive Builds, Elevate Your Gaming Fun</h2></strong><br>Character weapons can create different play styles. Various systems such as talents, artifacts, random affixes, abilities, and bonds, allow you to create unique builds that greatly increase the replayability of the game. After a few rounds of exploration, you could be the next speedrun champion! Random weapon bonuses and map elements add to the variety of combat.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2439710/extras/2f928789932aa676012e97ac9a4d5140.poster.avif?t=1727170517\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2439710/extras/2f928789932aa676012e97ac9a4d5140.webm?t=1727170517\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2439710/extras/2f928789932aa676012e97ac9a4d5140.mp4?t=1727170517\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Embrace fantastical  Monster Designs, Face Higher Challenges</h2></strong><br>Skybreakers immerses players in a captivating world a traditional ink-wash painting style. Players will gradually acquire resources and master various schools of secret arts to battle waves of evil creatures. Find your preferred fighting style, take on increasingly challenging levels, and experience a growing sense of excitement!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2439710/extras/c7cc9bac71a61abc7d9a1f5e58896594.poster.avif?t=1727170517\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2439710/extras/c7cc9bac71a61abc7d9a1f5e58896594.webm?t=1727170517\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2439710/extras/c7cc9bac71a61abc7d9a1f5e58896594.mp4?t=1727170517\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "∷ Indulge in fast-paced battles for an exhilarating combat experience.<br>∷ Choose from four unique characters to transform your gameplay experience.<br>∷ Craft varying battle experiences with 9 unique weapons tailored to each character.<br>∷ Forge a distinctive build through a rich mix of character talents, abilities, and artifacts.<br>∷ Enjoy the thrill of random weaon bonues and relentless reforging.<br>∷ Use your custom builds to climb the difficulty levels and confront a variety of mysterious monsters and Bosses.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2439710/extras/e8efe0862c8cae6003b7cd26bd59a445.poster.avif?t=1727170517\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2439710/extras/e8efe0862c8cae6003b7cd26bd59a445.webm?t=1727170517\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2439710/extras/e8efe0862c8cae6003b7cd26bd59a445.mp4?t=1727170517\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Strategize with Weapons, Customize Your Combat Style</h2></strong><br>The game features four distinct characters, each with 9 different weapons that can alter their moves. With 3 advanced effects for each type of attack - Basic Attack, Dash, and Ultimate - you can unleash multiple levels of damage, teleportation, disruption, buffs, and more. Engage in proactive combat and enjoy exhilarating, fast-paced battles.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2439710/extras/eece372556cb7d62382eaab372d096f5.poster.avif?t=1727170517\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2439710/extras/eece372556cb7d62382eaab372d096f5.webm?t=1727170517\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2439710/extras/eece372556cb7d62382eaab372d096f5.mp4?t=1727170517\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Forge Exclusive Builds, Elevate Your Gaming Fun</h2></strong><br>Character weapons can create different play styles. Various systems such as talents, artifacts, random affixes, abilities, and bonds, allow you to create unique builds that greatly increase the replayability of the game. After a few rounds of exploration, you could be the next speedrun champion! Random weapon bonuses and map elements add to the variety of combat.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2439710/extras/2f928789932aa676012e97ac9a4d5140.poster.avif?t=1727170517\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2439710/extras/2f928789932aa676012e97ac9a4d5140.webm?t=1727170517\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2439710/extras/2f928789932aa676012e97ac9a4d5140.mp4?t=1727170517\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Embrace fantastical  Monster Designs, Face Higher Challenges</h2></strong><br>Skybreakers immerses players in a captivating world a traditional ink-wash painting style. Players will gradually acquire resources and master various schools of secret arts to battle waves of evil creatures. Find your preferred fighting style, take on increasingly challenging levels, and experience a growing sense of excitement!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2439710/extras/c7cc9bac71a61abc7d9a1f5e58896594.poster.avif?t=1727170517\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2439710/extras/c7cc9bac71a61abc7d9a1f5e58896594.webm?t=1727170517\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2439710/extras/c7cc9bac71a61abc7d9a1f5e58896594.mp4?t=1727170517\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
